<h3 class="wikiHeadline3" id="H-NotableUpdates"><a href="/2012/03/14/aero-gear-100-m-2-released-more-mobile-goodness#H-NotableUpdates">Notable Updates</a></h3>

<b>Here are some of the notable updates to our core example and archetype:</b>

<ul class="wikiUnorderedList">
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Updates to our responsive design for better <a href="https://github.com/aerogear/as-quickstarts/blob/master/kitchensink-html5-mobile/src/main/webapp/index.html#L62" target="" class="regularLink">client and resolution</a> handling</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Updated look and feel for both desktop, and mobile interfaces.</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Added <a href="https://github.com/aerogear/as-quickstarts/blob/master/kitchensink-html5-mobile/SERVICES.md" target="" class="regularLink">JSONP support</a> for cross domain access to our endpoints.</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> <a href="https://community.jboss.org/en/tools/blog/2012/03/14/jboss-tools-and-developer-studio-beta1--chiliad" target="" class="regularLink">JBoss Tools 3.3 Beta1</a> integration with JBoss Central</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Integrated with <a href="https://www.redhat.com/openshift/community/blogs/new-openshift-release-march-5-2012-jboss-71-and-new-console" target="" class="regularLink">OpenShift's AS 7.1 cartridge</a> with deployment straight from JBoss Tools.</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Lots of updates to comments, and docs for better self explaining source</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Updated our <a href="http://poh5-aerogear.rhcloud.com/" target="" class="regularLink">live demo</a> showing this all on <a href="https://www.redhat.com/openshift/" target="" class="regularLink">OpenShift</a>
</li>
<li class="wikiUnorderedListItem"> Added our <a href="https://github.com/aerogear/as-quickstarts/tree/master/helloworld-html5" target="" class="regularLink">HelloWorld quickstart</a> to the mix</li>
</ul>

